<% @page_title = "Launching a server on Digital Ocean" %>
# Launching a server on Digital Ocean

<% spec = deployment_walkthrough_next_step_after_launching_server(locals) %>
On this page, we will launch a Digital Ocean server (or "droplets" as Digital Ocean calls them) and login to that server. If you have already launched a server, then you can [skip to the next page](<%= spec[:url] %>).

<div class="row row-instruction">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <p>
      Login to your Digital Ocean account click on <em>Create Droplet</em>.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <a href="<%= url_for("/walkthroughs/deploy/launch_server/digital_ocean_create_droplet.png") %>" target="_blank"><img src="<%= url_for("/walkthroughs/deploy/launch_server/digital_ocean_create_droplet.png") %>" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row row-instruction">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <p>
      Give your droplet a host name, then select an image. You are free to choose any Linux/Unix image, but for demonstration purposes let us pick the <em>Ubuntu 14.04 x64</em> image.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <a href="<%= url_for("/walkthroughs/deploy/launch_server/digital_ocean_image.png") %>" target="_blank"><img src="<%= url_for("/walkthroughs/deploy/launch_server/digital_ocean_image.png") %>" class="img-thumbnail" style="max-height: 15em"></a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row row-instruction">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <p>
      Select a droplet size. For smaller web apps, the 1 GB plan is enough.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <a href="<%= url_for("/walkthroughs/deploy/launch_server/digital_ocean_size.png") %>" target="_blank"><img src="<%= url_for("/walkthroughs/deploy/launch_server/digital_ocean_size.png") %>" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row row-instruction">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <p>
      Scroll down and click Create Droplet.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    <a href="<%= url_for("/walkthroughs/deploy/launch_server/digital_ocean_final.png") %>" target="_blank"><img src="<%= url_for("/walkthroughs/deploy/launch_server/digital_ocean_final.png") %>" class="img-thumbnail"></a>
  </div>
</div>

## Next step

Congratulations, you have launched a server on Digital Ocean and successfully logged in to the server!
